,"lifeSummary":"Lady Christina MacNaughton was born in 1247, in Scotland, United Kingdom. She married Alan MacDougall 7th. of Dunollie about 1290, in Argyll, Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in January 1310, in Craignish Castle, Argyll, Scotland, at the age of 63, and was buried in Argyll, Scotland."},"et":{"1247–January 1310":"1247–jaanuar 1310","1250–1350":"1250–1350","1267–1320":"1267–1320","1290–Male":"1290–Surnud","1270–1323":"1270–1323","1291–1354":"1291–1354","1292–Female":"1292–Surnud","1330–Female":"1330–Surnud","1247–1310":"1247–1310","about 1290":"umbes 1290","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","1250":"1250","1270":"1270","1292":"1292","1291":"1291","1390":"1390","1290":"1290","1247":"1247","January 1310":"jaanuar 1310","1323":"1323","1267":"1267","1310":"1310","1354":"1354","1320":"1320","Lorn, Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Craignish, Argyll, Scotland":"Craignish, Argyll, Scotland","Dunollie, Argyll, Scotland":"Dunollie, Argyll, Scotland","Craignish Castle, Argyll, Scotland":"Craignish Castle, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Craignish Castle, Craignish, Argyll, Scotland":"Craignish Castle, Argyll and Bute, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"fi":{"1247–January 1310":"1247–tammikuu 1310","1250–1350":"1250–1350","1267–1320":"1267–1320","1290–Male":"1290–Kuollut","1270–1323":"1270–1323","1291–1354":"1291–1354","1292–Female":"1292–Kuollut","1330–Female":"1330–Kuollut","1247–1310":"1247–1310","about 1290":"noin 1290","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","1250":"1250","1270":"1270","1292":"1292","1291":"1291","1390":"1390","1290":"1290","1247":"1247","January 1310":"tammikuu 1310","1323":"1323","1267":"1267","1310":"1310","1354":"1354","1320":"1320","Lorn, Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Craignish, Argyll, Scotland":"Craignish, Argyll, Scotland","Dunollie, Argyll, Scotland":"Dunollie, Argyll, Scotland","Craignish Castle, Argyll, Scotland":"Craignish Castle, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland